headline: Zacks Industry Outlook Highlights Aflac, Trupanion and Globe Life
summary: Zacks highlights Aflac, Trupanion, and Globe Life as key stocks in the accident & health insurance industry, which faces pricing pressure but benefits from tech adoption, underwriting strength, and growing demand.
